The '''Falling Leaf''', or '''Falling Avalanche''', was a [[Lightsaber combat/Legends|lightsaber combat]] technique that involved spinning on one's feet to "slash from the sky".<ref name="JK">''[[Dark Forces: Jedi Knight]]''</ref>

[[Kyle Katarn]] learned this technique by [[Force-bond/Legends|tapping on]] the [[Force ghost/Legends|spirit]] of [[Tal (Jedi)|Tal]] on [[Ruusan/Legends|Ruusan]] in [[5 ABY/Legends|5 ABY]]. Kyle used it to kill [[Jerec (Inquisitor)|Jerec]] after the latter tried to kill him, despite Kyle having offered him a chance to live.<ref name="JK" />

